data.description: This updated 2296 approx. sq. ft.,  3-4 BR home is located on an acre lot overlooking the farm fields in South Hanover.  The bright and welcoming living room has newer Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring.  The kitchen/dining room has ceramic tile flooring, granite counters, an island with seating, and a pantry closet for extra storage.  The owners bedroom has mirrored closets and a private bath with a shower and tile flooring.  The main level also  includes 2 more bedrooms and a hall bath with a skylight.  Downstairs you'll find a family room with a gas fireplace, windows for natural light and Pergo laminate flooring.  In the rear of the home is another large room, currently being used as an exercise room with a patio door to the deck and a walk-in closet.  Down the hall, the office/Bedroom 4 also has windows for natural light and a large closet.  The laundry room has cabinetry for storage.  A side loading one car garage with opener completes the lower level.  Outside you will find the insulated and anti-humidity finished Man Cave/She Shed currently housing a gym.  The rubber horse stall mat flooring, a pellet stove for heat and a window a/c unit is included with the man cave.  3 more sheds are included for your storage needs.  The yard features a garden area and 3 Asian pear trees that entice the deer to visit from the farmer's fields.
